Infernal Screamer (Requires 1 Crew and Grants Half Cover). The screamer's operator ta rgets one creature it can see within 120 feet of the screamer. The target must make a DC 15 Wisdom saving throw, taking 26 (4dl2) psychic damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</text>
