			<name>Crushing Wheels</name>
			<text>The Demon Grinder can move through the space of any Large or smaller creature. When it does, the creature must succeed on a DC 11 Dexterity saving throw or take 22 (4dl0) bludgeoning damage and be knocked prone. If the creature was already prone, it takes an extra 22 (4dl0) bludgeoning damage. This trait can't be used against a particular creature more than once each turn.</text>
